Use this file as a template for adding papers.

1. Copy this file to `_publications/YYYY-MM-DD-short-title.md`.
2. Replace the front matter values.
3. Set `category` to one of:
   - `preprints`
   - `manuscripts`
   - `conferences`
   - `posters`
4. Add an abstract, notes, code link, or PDF link below the front matter.
